### ============================================================================
### REPORTS — /api/v1/reports + /api/v1/plan-usage-ledgers
### ============================================================================

### ─── Reports — /api/v1/reports ─────────────────────────────

### Dashboard analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reports/dashboard/analytics?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Usage report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reports/usage?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Usage report CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reports/usage/csv?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Plan history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reports/plans?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Plan history CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reports/plans/csv?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Compliance report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reports/compliance?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Compliance report CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reports/compliance/csv?companyId={{companyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── Plan Usage Ledgers — /api/v1/plan-usage-ledgers ───────

### List all usage ledgers (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/plan-usage-ledgers?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get my usage ledgers (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/plan-usage-ledgers/my?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get usage ledgers by employee ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/plan-usage-ledgers/employee/{{employeeId}}?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get usage ledger by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/plan-usage-ledgers/{{planUsageLedgerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create usage ledger entry
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/plan-usage-ledgers
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": {{employeeId}},
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "companyId": {{companyId}},
  "planId": {{planId}},
  "action": "PLAN_CREATED",
  "creditsUsed": 1,
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.1",
  "userAgent": "Mozilla/5.0"
}

### Update usage ledger
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/plan-usage-ledgers/{{planUsageLedgerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "creditsUsed": 2,
  "action": "PLAN_GENERATED"
}

### Delete usage ledger
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/plan-usage-ledgers/{{planUsageLedgerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
